control not ebullient nor the quiet of worry said a senior 
us official who was at the table with bush aboard the maxim gorky 
he spoke in a very forthright manner about the economic 
problems he was up against his thoughts for tackling them his 
basic theme was ive got problems and im working on them the 
official recalled 
but when you look at the soviet problems the official said 
they are very deep and very broad 
