artist john feight who has designed thousands of murals for 
hospitals over the last 15 years said friday that he expects 4000 
people 1 percent of the shoppers expected at the lenox square 
mall next week to stop and color in a section of the 116 murals 
he has designed for the project 
sixteen of the murals identical pictures of the word love 
in russian and english joined by a heart will end up in hospitals 
in the soviet union the 49yearold founder of the foundation for 
hospital art said 
the rest various pictures of butterflies flowers and jungle 
scenes are destined for display in hospitals in bangladesh 
italy portugal austria zaire liberia and kenya as well as 
georgia baptist hospital in atlanta lake charles memorial hospital 
in louisiana and feights place of birth joel pomerene memorial 
hospital in millersburg ohio 
at the mall next week feight and volunteers will ask passersby 
to take a few minutes to help fill in the colors on the 4by6 foot 
loose canvas murals 
sometimes its not easy to get nonartists to take brush to 
hand he said 
theyre so innocent he said i go up to someone and say 
will you hold this please its a cup of paint and then i say 
now that you have this in your hand why dont you paint this 
space and they protest i cant paint i cant draw a straight 
line i havent taken any lessons 
but once they get into the idea that were helping people in 
hospitals they get into it they dont care its more than art 
its love 
the canvasses featuring love in english and russian were 
inspired by feights visit in april 1988 to the moscow research 
institute of eye microsurgery the patients there and staffers from 
the us embassy helped feight paint 37 murals on the walls of the 
hospital 
i did one mural that had the word love in russian feight 
recalled he said that prompted the hospitals director dr 
svyatoslav n fyodorov to remark thats what we need more of 
around here love 
that comment led to his latest project feight said 
he said he plans to take the 16 murals to moscow personally in 
early april from there fyodorov will distribute the murals to 
various hospitals in the soviet union 
while in moscow feight said he will direct the painting of 
similar murals by moscow residents those murals will be displayed 
at lenox square in april before going to various us hospitals 
